thread.title: TV | Modern Family

author: Fiona Flynn
title: TV | Modern Family
text: Brand new series of one of our all time favourite American comedies kicks off tonight. Things pick up directly after that season six finale cliffhanger where Phil realises that Andy and Hayley are in love with one another, only problem is, Andy is about to propose to his stupid not-right-for-him girlfriend. Can Phil let them know on time, or more importantly, will Hayley and Andy really be able to admit their feelings to each other?
